-mail server network. Chat with anyone if you know their e-mail address, no need for them to install DeltaChat, all you need is a standard e-mail account.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-22T13:14:47.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"croqaz/awesome-decentralized","categoryHTML":"<h3>Other</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://solidproject.org\">Solid</a>: Solid was created by the inventor of the World Wide Web, Sir Tim Berners-Lee. Solid is a specification that lets people store their data securely in decentralized data stores called Pods. Pods are like secure personal web servers for your data. For developer resources, see <a href=\"https://solidproject.org/developers\">Developer Resources</a>. For a listing of some Solid applications, see <a href=\"https://solidproject.org/apps\">Solid Applications</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-22T13:11:04.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"golemfactory/awesome-golem","categoryHTML":"<h2>Developer and Requestor Resources</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://yapapi.readthedocs.io/\">Yagna Python API docs</a> - Documentation for Yapapi.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-22T11:23:52.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"innocenzi/awesome-inertiajs","categoryHTML":"<h2>Adapters</h2><h3>Server-side</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jcs224/oak_inertia\">Oak (Deno)</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jcs224/oak_inertia\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":5,\"repo\":\"jcs224/oak_inertia\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO